-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">//Pegue os nós distribuídos</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> nodes <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> myContentObject<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getDistributedNodes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications_2","title":"Specificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"spec-table standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specificações</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/webcomponents/spec/shadow/#the-content-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Shadow DOM<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'content' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Obsoleto</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect2\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Componente</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari (WebKit)</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Supporte básico</td>\n   <td>35</td>\n   <td><span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/28\" title=\"Released on 2014-03-18.\">28</a> (28)</span>&nbsp;[1]</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>26</td>\n   <td><span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Phone</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>37</td>\n   <td>28.0 (28) [1]</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>[1] Se Shadow DOM não é&nbsp;habilitado&nbsp;no&nbsp;Firefox, <code>&lt;content&gt;</code> elementos se comportará&nbsp;como&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLUnknownElement\"><code>HTMLUnknownElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>. Shadow DOM foi primeiro implementado em&nbsp;Firefox 28 e está&nbsp;atrás de uma preferência, <code>dom.webcomponents.enabled</code>, ao qual é&nbsp;desabilitado por&nbsp;padrão.</p>"}},{